#' JASP Enhanced Bayesian Correlation
#'
#' jamovi-native shell for the JASP Bayesian correlation analysis.
#' @param data .
#' @param variables .
#' @param prior .
#' @param posterior .
#' @param apaReport .
#' @return A results object containing:
#' \tabular{llllll}{
